{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_03_01",
  "title": "kana 1話 恋愛解禁ってこと？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "何を暗い顔して、ため息ついてんのよ\nポンコツマネージャー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why the gloomy face and sighs?\nWhat a clumsy manager you are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6666667224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーがそんなだと\nアイドルにも伝染して、気分落ちるんですけど～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If the manager's like that‚\nthe mood of the idols will drop too‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.623180097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "仕事でポカしたとか？\n社長の逆鱗に触れて、明日にもクビになりそうとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you mess up at work or something?\nDid you incur the president's wrath and are on the verge of being fired tomorrow?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.400000469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "クビはまだ大丈夫なはずですけど\n実は、mihoさんとちょっと意見の相違が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I should be fine with the firing part…\nActually‚ I had a little disagreement with miho-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.200000469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリ歴代優勝者達の祭典？\nそんなんやるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The festival of the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix's past winners?\nThey're actually doing that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.6776185912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "はい、サニピと月ストには麻奈の曲を歌ってもらって\nmihoさんにはSundanceの曲をと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ we're having Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest sing Mana's songs‚\nand for miho-san‚ we're thinking of Sundance's songs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.7999997061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなん、あいつが出る訳ないじゃん\n長瀬麻奈もSundanceもmihoの地雷っしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no way she'd participate in that‚ right?\nBoth Nagase Mana and Sundance are landmines to miho.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.855785657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "興味ないkanaにだって分かるのに\nなんでmihoに話す前に気付かないかなぁ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even kana‚ who's not interested‚ can see that‚\nwhy didn't you notice it before talking to miho?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1794324162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……全部kanaさんの言う通りなんですが……\nmihoさんにはぜひ、出演してほしくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… It's all as you say‚ kana-san…\nBut I really want miho-san to participate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.3333330394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "あっそ。相変わらずメンドクサイ性格っていうか\nまぁ、kanaには関係ないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I see. You're as troublesome as ever.\nWell‚ it's none of kana's business‚ but‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2475275281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "……あのさぁ。前から思ってたんだけど\nあんた達、過去にこだわり過ぎじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "… You know‚ I've been thinking for a while‚\nAren't you guys too obsessed with the past?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8475275281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "特に長瀬麻奈のことになると、mihoも\n{user}も、みんな目つき変えちゃってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially when it comes to Nagase Mana‚ both miho\nand {user}‚ everyone changes their demeanor.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4141941948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "忘れろとまでは言わないけど\nもっと未来を見た方が良くない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not saying to forget about it completely‚\nbut shouldn't you focus more on the future?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.5141941948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "あんたはマネージャーなんだから\n今いるアイドルを大事に考えるべきなんじゃないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're a manager‚ after all.\nShouldn't you prioritize the idols you have now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.4475275281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……確かに麻奈は俺にとって特別な存在です\nでも、決して他のアイドルをないがしろになんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Indeed‚ Mana is a special presence to me.\nBut by no means would I neglect other idols…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.5666704417,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、なんでいつまでも長瀬麻奈に固執するかな～\nあっ、もしかして、付き合ってたとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then why are you so obsessed with Nagase Mana forever?\nOh‚ could it be you two were dating or something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.790846091,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、ちょっと待って下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ wait a minute!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3528340263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "きゃはっ、マジで？　二人ってそんな関係だったの？\nおいおい、公私混同かよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaha‚ seriously? Were you two really in that kind of relationship?\nGeez‚ mixing business with personal life…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.3613064813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "自分が担当してるアイドルに手を出すとかキモっ！\nSNSで呟いちゃおうかな～。絶対バズるじゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's creepy to get involved with idols you're managing!\nShould I post it on social media? It'll definitely go viral!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.0520643475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "あーでも、スリクスのマネージャーのスキャンダルとか\nkanaにとってはマイナスかな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ but a scandal involving IIIX's manager‚\nmight be a negative for kana~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.1502653432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ、kanaさん、やめて下さい！\nここは事務所ですし……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ kana-san‚ could you please stop!\nThis is the office‚ you know…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.3020628852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "はあ？　どこで何を話そうがkanaの\n勝手なんですけど～？　命令しないでくれます～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Where and what kana talk about is\nnone of your business‚ right? Can't I do what I want?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.4993432286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、場所を変えましょう。お願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ let's change the location. Please!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.032675036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　移動するの面倒なんだけど～\nあっ、でも、ちょっとノド乾いたかも～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? I don't feel like moving though~\nAh‚ but I'm feeling a bit thirsty~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.391541187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "SNS映えしそうなオシャレなドリンク、飲みたいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to drink a stylish drink that'll look good on social media~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.5336498819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いいカフェを探します！　一緒に行きましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll find a nice café! Let's go together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.3336498819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.4293186588
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.4293186588
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "――という訳で、俺も初めての担当アイドルで\n思い入れがあるんです……って聞いてます？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――So‚ I also have a special attachment to my first idol\nI'm managing…. Do you hear me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.0304962714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan019.m4a",
      "text": "聞いてる聞いてる\nていうか、ドリンクも店も普通過ぎない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ yeah‚ I'm listening.\nBut‚ isn't the drink and the store a bit too ordinary?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.5706578973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 195.4706563714
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
